issue.title: Fix/food categories
issue.body:
- Sorted emojis into three categories: drinks, mains and desserts.
- Moved instructive texts upward along the Y-axis for better visibility.
- Compressed textures and reduced file size to 2MB and lower for iOS, Android and older Android.

issue.title: Feature/headmovement
issue.body:
The feature update has:
* changing choices based on head shake.
* jackpot showing based on head nod.

Needs:
* After the head nod the jackpot is more like a switch, it doesn't reset and the text still remains on the screen until the next head nod
